headline: These 3 stocks are soaring as the U.S. rushes to patch its electrical grid
summary: Much of the grid was built over 50 years ago, and AI data centers are just one reason energy demand has skyrocketed.

headline: Quanta (PWR): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: Quanta currently trades at $325.42 and has been a dream stock for shareholders. It’s returned 697% since December 2019, blowing past the S&P 500’s 85.6% gain. The company has also beaten the index over the past six months as its stock price is up 21.9% thanks to its solid quarterly results.
